:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"咪返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1913946e073424a443925e1bc979e2c61a6524e","tid":2360124,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"問我就岩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e61e216eebbf4950ca69641c9323d96d4045c9","tid":2360124,"uid":229397,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"我之前是在加油站打工的，而我加油的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘加爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘加爆，老子才不管甚麼公司虧損三小的，每次加的油就是機掰一大箱。機車加成大客車，小客車加成連結車。卡車加成遠洋漁船，連結車加成空中巴士大飛機，跟把整個加油站的石油全送給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月石油虧損兩萬六千桶，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"30b24f8b27eff1b8876b786b9ac043edeef9f33a","tid":2360124,"uid":23546,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9a9fed022505111d5fe4820fb59c8d2f618d6029","tid":2360124,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce89a9f800d2cfad233f4b78c3083fa9ce12ce8d","tid":2360124,"uid":229397,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8528e0db8e58fd2245db47202ed1ddb44718d07c","tid":2360124,"uid":23546,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T13:35:09.000Z","msg":"銀碼唔好搞錯<br />\n唔好入錯油（我之前做嗰間如果打滿嘅話係唔駛set油品，有機會抆錯槍入錯油，通常都係柴油車入錯電油）<br />\n入完油記得擰油蓋<br />\n油站又辛苦又人工低，真係唔建議做"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"好撚同意, 人工低冇前途, 做錯嘢奶嘢會好甘, 行頭又窄, 日更多嘢做夜更唔抵做。pt都係咁話。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"奴工法例最多賠3舊<br />\n拉利入左油渣會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"唔會架，油渣支槍督唔入電油車缸，加上見到貴車會格外留神冇咩可能出事"},{"pid":"8232ab35de46efac643a03a9815c446d43c383ec","tid":2360124,"uid":23546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a3dfb37ba0f8de0f147a74a9aba26807f2df06ea","tid":2360124,"uid":72751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8528e0db8e58fd2245db47202ed1ddb44718d07c","tid":2360124,"uid":23546,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"a8bc4205806acf666ed05f1e21a5146d8a09fb00","tid":2360124,"uid":387286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"想去油站做兼職 有冇咩要注意⚠️<br />\n或者可以提點下我<br />\n到時入去做都可以醒目d<br />\n感恩"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T13:35:09.000Z","msg":"銀碼唔好搞錯<br />\n唔好入錯油（我之前做嗰間如果打滿嘅話係唔駛set油品，有機會抆錯槍入錯油，通常都係柴油車入錯電油）<br />\n入完油記得擰油蓋<br />\n油站又辛苦又人工低，真係唔建議做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"睇下做咩區喇 某d區夜更 游撚到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"做過中半山區，成晚十架車都冇<br />\n<br />\n混合站千祈唔好做，做到仆晒街"},{"pid":"5aeb0eed4139e6f9aaeb3b013fb6a1e14e134b80","tid":2360124,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"有冇超跑車主會自己入 或者落車𥄫到實<br />\n好撚大壓力"},{"pid":"c658330fd40ab6584974c991d388cea6551e42eb","tid":2360124,"uid":11849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"唔好入錯油, 後果嚴重<br />\n入幾多要聽清楚/double confirm<br />\n入完check清楚支油槍安全鎖, 試過幾次一拎支槍出嚟係咁噴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加水唔好拎錯蓋<br />\n幫客買完箱水記得收錢<br />\n油站唔好揀西斜, 會生熱痱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c7d33d655479e37c3c27a4d9d1b759e379be4c","tid":2360124,"uid":111193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"763ea4c3737329d6228ca74173ee2930cab052ea","tid":2360124,"uid":109977,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"有冇同事叫呀木？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cb184ac49885136cf247800b4989f2990f3f98","tid":2360124,"uid":23546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aeb0eed4139e6f9aaeb3b013fb6a1e14e134b80","tid":2360124,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"有冇超跑車主會自己入 或者落車𥄫到實<br />\n好撚大壓力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"好多都會，如果幫佢入我會親手揸住支槍直至入完<br />\n因為有機會油缸有氣會喺支槍停之前嗝油出嚟"},{"pid":"a2e01b3321754a2c85102fcb63b378108c93af37","tid":2360124,"uid":229397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇超跑車主會<span class=\"blue\">自己入</span> 或者<span class=\"red\">落車𥄫到實</span><br />\n好撚大壓力</blockquote><br />\n一樣米百樣人, <span class=\"blue\">藍色字</span>未必有, 就算有都應該未必會批准佢咁做。就算識自己入都未必識用油鎗入。<br />\n但<span class=\"red\">紅色字</span>發生既機率會高好多, 就算唔落車都會𥄫到實, 而且有唔少恃住自己有幾個臭<span class=\"orange\">＄</span>就會有唔同程度既口氣。不過, 只要係服務&middot;性行業都會遇到各式有<span class=\"orange\">＄</span>或窮既閪客。"},{"pid":"b3a9f371f2eec175d70529cbff941b1929c1a4b7","tid":2360124,"uid":229397,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"其實點解返PT會去揀啲咁既嘢? 好似返樓面/便利店呢啲做PT好似會好啲。體驗多嘢做人工低或許對將來有幫助。<br />\nPT我做過樓面火煱, sofar都算好做, 係試過跣低過1次, 跣咗碟成千銀既肥牛落地啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5def8f9c8da058d0af7e7524c74d10f1ab37ecc2","tid":2360124,"uid":199227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T18:13:52.000Z","msg":"最近要去屏山喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8598383457a537d59093e1fa8416d678619fcb","tid":2360124,"uid":140140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T19:03:10.000Z","msg":"無得食煙"},{"pid":"e5863dade28d4a1b7c5e2af39d6b80e19d4f9f40","tid":2360124,"uid":353358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T19:28:29.000Z","msg":"香港做油站好多都無車，賤過地底泥既垃圾，本身應該要全家折肢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc9e450fc15cd207d26e4a0df6a1ed432f5118d","tid":2360124,"uid":283385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8bc4205806acf666ed05f1e21a5146d8a09fb00","tid":23601